Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Signs
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Opening
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ending
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.35,0:00:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.41,0:00:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're from Mistral? That place sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it has great food and a ton of hot chicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.43,0:01:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been almost six months since the armistice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.46,0:01:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta thank my lucky stars that I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready to get up, missy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.70,0:01:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll share my booty with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.86,0:01:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caramel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't accept something so expensive...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you don't give the trumpeters a hard time,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make sure you hear the withdrawal signal loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.15,0:01:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't see too many new recruits nowadays, what with the draft being over and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a volunteer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I want to learn music!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.06,0:01:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, honesty's the best policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.75,0:01:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, missy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:01:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name, private?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorami Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's going to be a festival in Seize today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A festival!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll be taking my leave of you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where you've been assigned to. It's called the Time-Keeping Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find a way there by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.36,0:04:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Sorami Kanata will be assigned to the 1221st Platoon in Seize, Trois.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Republic of Helvetia Army Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1320, mission completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.79,0:05:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seize, the city of springs and glass...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to report in at 1500 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finally be able to play music with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Route check, complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time check, complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.49,0:05:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Equipment check, complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D flat... what a wonderful note.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, a fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,$12.25...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... What a beautiful doll-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A kitten got lost amid all the hustle and bustle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, kittens just love wandering around all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would agree if it had been a wild cat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.22,0:07:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, this one was a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That really startled me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found something fabulous, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How may I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, a soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she from the fortress?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we'll have a good fortune for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you get me wet!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you retarded?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're frickin' soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is wrong with you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, watch i-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.73,0:09:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tha...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Christ... Come on, follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the temperature?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's a pretty easy target...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you not even try to dodge them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This type of fabric is very easy to clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,0:09:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a festival, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:09:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it originated from a legend we have here in Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maidens of flame protecting the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the imposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The maintenence is complete, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Felicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That busybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's late...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's late! She's late! She's late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came all the way here to welcome her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just calm down and wait patiently, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't your dad give this to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for letting me use your bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.63,0:11:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... kind of have a tendency to get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's why I met awesome people like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to get lost, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you recognize notes easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound is very clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's somehow comforting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.31,0:11:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.65,0:11:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:12:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God damn... is that thing worth more than your life!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure this is okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to leave. I have something to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.68,0:12:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bell must've been really precious to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.94,0:12:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:12:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.41,0:14:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maidens of flame?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long, long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long before the world became like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a winged demon lived in the ravines of this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It showered fire down upon the land,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,bringing great suffering to the people who lived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.59,0:14:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It kidnapped the maidens who lived here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.43,0:14:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and imprisoned them in an underground labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the maidens did not despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:15:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They called upon one another using the golden horn bestowed upon them by the Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.20,0:15:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and thus escaped the labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They defeated the demon and took its head
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by borrowing the power of a great spider.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, the head would not cease spewing its flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.01,0:15:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it had continued to do so, then the entire city would have been engulfed by fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.66,0:15:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, in order to halt the flames,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the maidens took turns embracing the demon's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people of the city poured water upon the maidens every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After a year, the fire was finally extinguished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we've held the water festival in order to appease the souls of the maidens who saved the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the recruit's not coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,0:16:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, look at Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How very fitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we made the right decision in letting her handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:16:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't we draw lots...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.66,0:17:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.70,0:17:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pretty much suck, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have fun when I get lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but only because I meet people I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want my mommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.97,0:17:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you keep believing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.82,0:17:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your feelings will reach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, your sound will resound without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:17:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll resound...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It shall resound without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And reach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.01,0:18:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maiden of flame, rest here in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Embrace the demon and appease the curse...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that it will never again awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The golden horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.90,0:18:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the demon arisen!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let my sound reach someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It reached someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will resound and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake your ass up, Private Sorami Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.41,0:19:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how long were you planning to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.71,0:19:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Time-Keeping Fortress, the garrison of the 1221st Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to apologize for what happened yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'm just giving you a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so reckless in the future, though, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.79,0:19:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, this is just an ordinary bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How to play trumpet!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...why this fortress is known as the Time-Keeping Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the sound of the skies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazumiya Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be your trumpet instructor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to working with you, Sergeant Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.13,0:21:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:22:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Felicia- the captain wants us to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't address each other with military ranks here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.93,0:22:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.09,0:22:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about Ms. Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.77,0:22:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go ahead and get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.08,0:22:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me hear a wake-up call!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.56,0:22:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever's playing now is terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.88,0:24:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: First Campaign: The Story of the Chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.31,0:02:12.22,Anime Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\pos(951,432)\fad(0,2500)}Sound of the Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:55.32,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(918,384)}Resounding Note \N The Street of Daybreak
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.94,0:24:34.99,Ed Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\pos(656,84)}First Campaign:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.94,0:24:34.99,Ed Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\pos(662,251)}The Story of the Chair
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.96,0:02:21.31,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Does the radiance from the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:26.54,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}reach all the way to your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:36.43,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}The melody I heard in my dream reminds me of a calm night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:41.53,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Even when your hands are still so far away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:46.55,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}I hope you'll still recall that gentle voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:59.40,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}It's the blissful chord someone sang for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:03.73,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}May the sound of the sky ring far and wide,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:08.74,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}up and over all the sorrows gelid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:19.34,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Only the real world reflects in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:28.73,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Not even tears can bind you in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:34.02,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Within the overflowing light,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:41.00,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}may you play out the morrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:51.25,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Let's get friendship, love, and other feelings together,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.51,0:22:54.58,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}and play out how important they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.74,0:23:12.53,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}I cried from joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.56,0:23:18.55,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}I laughed from pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:24.53,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}But that's all a part of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.64,0:23:27.35,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}and tells me that I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:31.97,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Let's take this slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.73,0:23:33.55,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Everybody singing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.58,0:23:38.06,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Can you tell me how you really feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.71,0:23:39.16,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}You're just my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.18,0:23:44.90,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Even when friendship and love waver,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.19,0:23:45.18,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}I know, you know, will be happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.13,0:23:50.87,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}I hope this melody will ring forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.97,0:23:51.07,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Can you count my precious flower
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.10,0:23:57.01,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Overflowing words are hardly enough to describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.11,0:24:02.88,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}This is our harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.04,0:24:07.84,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\org(0,0)\fad(120,120)}Can you hear our harmony?
